        "title": "Summary",
        "content": "| Priority | Scope | Files | Coverage |\n|----------|-------|-------|----------|\n| P0 — Now | Core crypto + EventBus | `HistoryOfThought`, `EventBus` | 0% → target 80% |\n| P1 — Next | Executive layer | `ExecutiveSpine`, `SovereignRouter` | 0% → target 80% |\n| P2 — Then | Services | `SovereignReconciler`, `BriefService`, `ChatService` | 0% → target 70% |\n| P3 — Later | Integration flows | 3 flows above | 0% → target 60% |\n| P4 — Future | Frontend components | 32 components | 0% → target 50% |\n\nThe crypto and audit trail code (`HistoryOfThought` + `EventBus`) is the highest risk with zero coverage — a silent encryption bug there destroys the entire authenticity model. Start there.",
        "level": 2
      }
